metadata.name: target, Zhao Zhiguo pulled
metadata.description:
decisively!



The sound of the gun rang through the ancient earth, the bullet tore the air, flew toward the target, a small devil fell to the sound.



"Yi... A surprise?"



The bullet did not hit Zhao Zhiguo selected the target, in the target behind the small devil was shot down. Originally Zhao Zhiguo just wanted to test the gun, to feel the temper of the gun, did not expect......



"There was a problem with the base line, but the bullet flew fairly steadily. At 400 meters, the bullet didn't drop much, so it seems that you need to aim to the left... One more shot!"
